Slice - attack skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Slice is the most basic of attack skills learned by a
budding, young swashbuckler. Using a slashing main blade,
the swashbuckler slices at his opponent in an attempt to
inflict a fatal wound. While not a particularly elegant
attack, a well-timed slice can be effective at dispatching
a weakened enemy. This attack can only be attemped once
per opponent though, as they will quickly catch on to
the swashbuckler's tricks. Note that this attack is much
more effective as a final, killing stroke on an enemy near
death.

GL:  1
SP: 10
command: sslice <target> (defaults to opponent if in combat)
duration: instant
